<bold>How do you contribute towards eye care services in rural and peri-urban areas</bold>
</p><table-wrap position="anchor" id="d67e1661"><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><tbody><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x02611; Capacity building</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; Strategic planning</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; Fundraising</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; Training</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; Education</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; Raising public awareness (advocacy)</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; Performing surgeries</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; Screening patients</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; Providing expert opinion for complex cases</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; Connecting with partners/donors</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; Developing/designing policies and regulatory frameworks</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; Healthcare financial auditing</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x025a1; <inline-graphic xlink:href="IJO-72-473-g008.jpg"/></td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"/></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap><table-wrap position="anchor" id="d67e1699"><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><tbody><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">
